WEBVTT

00:12:57.796 --> 00:13:01.230
so it helps the citizen
to put him- or herself

00:13:01.230 --> 00:13:03.902
in other people's place.

00:13:03.902 --> 00:13:07.170
And that idea, I think, 
should be the intention,

00:13:07.170 --> 00:13:11.885
should be the goal of any good journalism,
any good activism,

00:13:11.885 --> 00:13:14.537
but most of all, any good politics.

00:13:14.537 --> 00:13:17.065
Thank you very much. It was an honor.

00:13:17.065 --> 00:13:22.708
(Applause)